te?":false,"vulnerability_information":"Hey, I've found *email spoofing* vulnerability in support@veris.in \nIssue:\n========\nWhen I try to send a fake email from support@veris.in  to my email (mrahsan1337@gmail.com) I was successful in sending a fake email to my **inbox**, this is an issue; because, fake mails should be sent into the 'spam' folder.\n\n### Exploit Code:\n```\n\u003c?php\n$to = \"mrahsan1337@gmail.com\";\n$subject = \"test by ahsan\";\n$txt = \"testing\";\n$headers = \"From: support@veris.in\";\nmail($to,$subject,$txt,$headers);\n?\u003e\n```\nWhen I tried to run it as a web-app in my browser, like, I created a file in my server (e.g test.php) and in that file I put this exploit code, and saved it when i run it like myserver.com/test.php it showed a blank white page, and next i checked out my email and i received an email from support@veris.in into my **inbox** saying 'testing' \n\nI hope you'll fix it soon.. :-)\n\nThanks,\nAhsan Tahir","vulnerability_information_html":"\u003cp\u003eHey, I\u0026#39;ve found \u003cem\u003eemail spoofing\u003c/em\u003e vulnerability in \u003ca title=\"support@veris.in\" href=\"mailto:support@veris.in\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"\u003esupport@veris.in\u003c/a\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch1 id=\"issue\"\u003eIssue:\u003c/h1\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWhen I try to send a fake email from \u003ca title=\"support@veris.in\" href=\"mailto:support@veris.in\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"\u003esupport@veris.in\u003c/a\u003e  to my email (\u003ca title=\"mrahsan1337@gmail.com\" href=\"mailto:mrahsan1337@gmail.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"\u003emrahsan1337@gmail.com\u003c/a\u003e) I was successful in sending a fake email to my \u003cstrong\u003einbox\u003c/strong\u003e, this is an issue; because, fake mails should be sent into the \u0026#39;spam\u0026#39; folder.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"exploit-code\"\u003eExploit Code:\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"highlight\"\u003e\u003cpre class=\"highlight php\"\u003e\u003ccode\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cp\"\u003e\u0026lt;?php\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"nv\"\u003e$to\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"s2\"\u003e\u0026quot;mrahsan1337@gmail.com\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e;\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"nv\"\u003e$subject\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"s2\"\u003e\u0026quot;test by ahsan\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e;\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"nv\"\u003e$txt\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"s2\"\u003e\u0026quot;testing\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e;\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"nv\"\u003e$headers\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"s2\"\u003e\u0026quot;From: support@veris.in\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e;\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"nb\"\u003email\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e(\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nv\"\u003e$to\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e,\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nv\"\u003e$subject\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e,\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nv\"\u003e$txt\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e,\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nv\"\u003e$headers\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e);\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"cp\"\u003e?\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhen I tried to run it as a web-app in my browser, like, I created a file in my server (e.g test.php) and in that file I put this exploit code, and saved it when i run it like myserver.com/test.php it showed a blank white page, and next i checked out my email and i received an email from \u003ca title=\"support@veris.in\" href=\"mailto:support@veris.in\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"\u003esupport@veris.in\u003c/a\u003e into my \u003cstrong\u003einbox\u003c/strong\u003e saying \u0026#39;testing\u0026#39; \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eI hope you\u0026#39;ll fix it soon.. :-)\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThanks,\u003cbr\u003e\nAhsan Tahir\u003c/p\u003e\n","weakness":{"id":48,"name":"Denial of Service"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[],"allow_singular_disclosure_at":"2016-08-03T10:43:29.611Z","allow_singular_disclosure_after":-138995292.7364174,"singular_disclosure_allowed":true,"vote_count":8,"voters":["vichaarya","ahsan","spetr0x","hackworld","trabajoduro_2","dyabla","fwblen","mfrost"],"structured_scope":null,"abilities":{"assignable_team_members":[],"assignable_team_member_groups":[]},"can_edit_custom_fields_attributes":false,"activities":[{"id":1048732,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::Comment","message":"Thanks @ahsantahirat for the report. We would look into it.","markdown_message":"\u003cp\u003eThanks \u003ca href=\"/ahsantahirat\"\u003e@ahsantahirat\u003c/a\u003e for the report. We would look into it.\u003c/p\u003e\n","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2016-07-01T07:41:48.874Z","updated_at":"2016-07-01T07:41:48.874Z","actor":{"username":"veris-nayan","cleared":false,"url":"/veris-nayan","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"/assets/avatars/default-71a302d706457f3d3a31eb30fa3e73e6cf0b1d677b8fa218eaeaffd67ae97918.png"},"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":false},"genius_execution_id":null,"team_handle":"veris","actor_is_team_member":true,"actor_is_concealed_member":true},{"id":1048734,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::BugDuplicate","message":"","markdown_message":"","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2016-07-01T07:42:18.435Z","updated_at":"2016-07-01T07:42:18.435Z","original_report_id":144450,"actor":{"username":"veris-nayan","cleared":false,"url":"/veris-nayan","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"/assets/avatars/defaul